class="card card-featured"><h1 class="card-title">
Milkshake Website Examples - 10 Sweet Sites That Entice New Customers</h1><div
class="card-body"><div
class="card-text card-text-prebyline">10 visually appealing milkshake websites that draw attention and sell the business.</div><div
class="card-byline"><div
class="card-byline-image">
<img
class="lazyload"
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-simone-gambrell-800x800-2024057.webp?crop=1:1,smart&width=80&dpr=2"
width="80"
height="80"
alt="Simoné Gambrell"
/></div><div
class="card-byline-details">
<span>By <a
class="card-byline-author" href="https://www.zarla.com/contributors/simoné-gambrell">Simoné Gambrell</a>,</span>
<span
class="card-byline-date">Jul 22, 2024</span><div
class="card-byline-bio">
Simoné Gambrell is a Copywriter based in South Africa. She has enjoyed using her creativity to research and write articles about logos for small businesses since 2019.</div></div></div></div><div
class="card-image-holder"><div
class="card-preview">
<picture>
<source
srcset="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-milkshake-website-examples-6000x4000-20240513.jpeg?crop=2:1,smart&width=372 1x, https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-milkshake-website-examples-6000x4000-20240513.jpeg?crop=2:1,smart&width=372&dpr=2 2x"
