class="entry-content"><div
class="entry-content-section"><h3 id="magic-milkshakes-more" class="entry-website-title">Magic Milkshakes &amp; More</h3><div
class="entry-website-img"><div
class="entry-faux-browser"><div
class="entry-browser-menu"><div
class="dot"></div><div
class="dot"></div><div
class="dot"></div></div>
<picture>
<source
data-srcset="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-magic-milkshakes-20240527-desktop.webp?crop=2:1,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=332&dpr=2" media="(max-width: 412px)" />
<source
data-srcset="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-magic-milkshakes-20240527-desktop.webp?crop=400:248,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=495&dpr=2" media="(max-width: 575px)" />
<img
class="lazyload"
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-magic-milkshakes-20240527-desktop.webp?crop=400:248,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=650&dpr=2"
width="650"
height="403"
alt="desktop screenshot of website Magic Milkshakes &amp; More"
/>
</picture></div></div><p
class="entry-website-detail website-detail-url">
<span
class="icon">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-link.svg" alt="chain icon" width="29" height="29" />
</span>
<a
class="force-single-line" href="https://magicmilkshakesmore.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">
https://magicmilkshakesmore.com/
</a></p><p
class="entry-website-detail website-detail-location">
<span
class="icon">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-pin.svg" alt="pin icon" width="30" height="30" />
</span>
<span>Hoover, Alabama, U.S.</span></p><div
class="entry-text"><p>Magic Milkshake &amp; More is a family-owned business specializing in milkshakes, ice creams, brownies, waffles, sundaes, and more. Visitors to the site will notice a unique setup that organizes the information into menu and store information on the left, and business information and social media links in a drop-down menu on the right.</p><p>This layout makes it easy for visitors to quickly access the information they need, including reserving a private party, reading about the business, and seeing enticing milkshake images with descriptions of the menu items. However, the site does lack allergy information.</p></div><h4>Pros and Cons</h4><div
class="entry-indented-box"><div
class="entry-website-pros">
<span
class="icon icon-sm">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-plus.svg" alt="plus sign" width="18" height="18" />
</span><div
class="entry-text"><p>WAVE reports only 5 errors on the site, including missing alternative text, empty buttons, and one contrast error. This site scores highly on PageSpeed Insights and uses bright colors and images to stand out.</p></div></div><div
class="entry-website-cons">
<span
class="icon icon-sm">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-minus.svg" alt="minus sign" width="18" height="18" />
</span><div
class="entry-text"><p>According to WAVE, the site is only semi-compliant with assistive technologies. Some of the images, particularly of the location, are poor quality, which seems like an oversight for a website that seeks to showcase the edible items.</p></div></div></div><h4>Desktop Review</h4><div
class="entry-website-desktop"><div
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-magic-milkshakes-20240527-desktop.webp"
data-type="desktop"
class="lightbox-trigger js-lightbox-trigger"
><div
class="lightbox-thumbnail">
<img
class="lazyload"
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-magic-milkshakes-20240527-desktop.webp?crop=400:248,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=400&dpr=2"
alt="desktop screenshot of website"
width="400"
height="248"
/></div>
<img
class="lightbox-thumbnail-magnifier"
src="/assets/images/icon-magnifying.svg"
alt="magnifying glass"
width="50"
height="50"
/></div><div
class="entry-text"><p>The desktop site makes good use of the larger screen sizes, grid layout, and clear menu navigation to organize information in easy-to-view sizes, making legibility easier for visitors to the site. On Google's PageSpeed Insights, while there is room for improvement with the accessibility of the desktop, the site scores 98/100 for overall performance.</p></div></div><h4>Mobile Review</h4><div
class="entry-website-mobile"><div
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-magic-milkshakes-20240527-mobile.webp"
data-type="mobile"
class="lightbox-trigger js-lightbox-trigger"
><div
class="lightbox-thumbnail">
<img
class="lazyload"
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-magic-milkshakes-20240527-mobile.webp?crop=3:5,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=375&dpr=2"
alt="mobile screenshot of website"
width="325"
height="542"
/></div>
<img
class="lightbox-thumbnail-magnifier"
src="/assets/images/icon-magnifying.svg"
alt="magnifying glass"
width="50"
height="50"
/></div><div
class="entry-text"><p>Navigation on the mobile site is slightly different, with all the pages arranged under a hamburger menu to the left. Images are also better sized to the mobile screen so visitors can view the full image at once as opposed to scrolling to see the whole image on the desktop. The mobile site has a performance score of 83/100 on PageSpeed Insights, due to a slower blocking time than on the desktop site.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div
class="entry-container entry-container-content"><div
class="entry-content-wrapper"><div
class="entry-content"><div
class="entry-content-section"><h3 id="soda-jerk-co" class="entry-website-title">Soda Jerk Co.</h3><div
class="entry-website-img"><div
class="entry-faux-browser"><div
class="entry-browser-menu"><div
class="dot"></div><div
class="dot"></div><div
class="dot"></div></div>
<picture>
<source
data-srcset="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-soda-jerk-20240527-desktop.webp?crop=2:1,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=332&dpr=2" media="(max-width: 412px)" />
<source
data-srcset="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-soda-jerk-20240527-desktop.webp?crop=400:248,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=495&dpr=2" media="(max-width: 575px)" />
<img
class="lazyload"
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-soda-jerk-20240527-desktop.webp?crop=400:248,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=650&dpr=2"
width="650"
height="403"
alt="desktop screenshot of website Soda Jerk Co."
/>
</picture></div></div><p
class="entry-website-detail website-detail-url">
<span
class="icon">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-link.svg" alt="chain icon" width="29" height="29" />
</span>
<a
class="force-single-line" href="https://sodajerkco.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">
https://sodajerkco.com/
</a></p><p
class="entry-website-detail website-detail-location">
<span
class="icon">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-pin.svg" alt="pin icon" width="30" height="30" />
</span>
<span>Phoenix, Arizona, U.S.</span></p><div
class="entry-text"><p>Soda Jerk is a milkshake bar that uses local ingredients and creative family recipes to create unique milkshakes that are served with friendly hospitality. The simple design of the site allows visitors to find essential information, including the menu, location, hours, gift cards, and job opportunities all in the traditional website menu.</p><p>While visitors can scroll down to see contact details and social media links, the site does lack some nice-to-know information, such as allergens, possibilities for party rentals, and online ordering options.</p></div><h4>Pros and Cons</h4><div
class="entry-indented-box"><div
class="entry-website-pros">
<span
class="icon icon-sm">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-plus.svg" alt="plus sign" width="18" height="18" />
</span><div
class="entry-text"><p>WAVE reports only one missing form label and two contrast errors on the site indicating great accessibility. High-quality images shine on the site, enticing customers with photos of delicious milkshakes.</p></div></div><div
class="entry-website-cons">
<span
class="icon icon-sm">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-minus.svg" alt="minus sign" width="18" height="18" />
</span><div
class="entry-text"><p>The site is only semi-compliant with assistive technologies and lacks additional information, such as allergy information, loyalty programs, party reservations, and an "about the business" section.</p></div></div></div><h4>Desktop Review</h4><div
class="entry-website-desktop"><div
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-soda-jerk-20240527-desktop.webp"
data-type="desktop"
class="lightbox-trigger js-lightbox-trigger"
><div
class="lightbox-thumbnail">
<img
class="lazyload"
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-soda-jerk-20240527-desktop.webp?crop=400:248,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=400&dpr=2"
alt="desktop screenshot of website"
width="400"
height="248"
/></div>
<img
class="lightbox-thumbnail-magnifier"
src="/assets/images/icon-magnifying.svg"
alt="magnifying glass"
width="50"
height="50"
/></div><div
class="entry-text"><p>The desktop site welcomes visitors with a great, bright, and enticing hero image, encouraging customers to scroll down and find out more about the business and the menu offerings. The font and color palette used complement the milkshake theme wonderfully.</p><p>According to Google's PageSpeed Insights report, the desktop site makes great use of SEO, receiving a score of 100/100, while some potential to save on space leads to an overall performance score of 89/100.</p></div></div><h4>Mobile Review</h4><div
class="entry-website-mobile"><div
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-soda-jerk-20240527-mobile.webp"
data-type="mobile"
class="lightbox-trigger js-lightbox-trigger"
><div
class="lightbox-thumbnail">
<img
class="lazyload"
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-soda-jerk-20240527-mobile.webp?crop=3:5,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=375&dpr=2"
alt="mobile screenshot of website"
width="325"
height="542"
/></div>
<img
class="lightbox-thumbnail-magnifier"
src="/assets/images/icon-magnifying.svg"
alt="magnifying glass"
width="50"
height="50"
/></div><div
class="entry-text"><p>The mobile site is well-optimized to the smaller screens, with the images looking better in the smaller, well-framed sizes. With the traditional menu collapsed into the hamburger menu, navigation remains the same as the desktop, with the contact details and social media links at the bottom of the pages.</p><p>While the mobile site maintains high scores for SEO and best practices on PageSpeed Insights, slower loading times with larger content have lowered the overall performance score to 33/100.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div
class="entry-container entry-container-content"><div
class="entry-content-wrapper"><div
class="entry-content"><div
class="entry-content-section"><h3 id="the-crazy-mason" class="entry-website-title">The Crazy Mason</h3><div
class="entry-website-img"><div
class="entry-faux-browser"><div
class="entry-browser-menu"><div
class="dot"></div><div
class="dot"></div><div
class="dot"></div></div>
<picture>
<source
data-srcset="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-websiteexample-thecrazymason-20240522-desktop.webp?crop=2:1,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=332&dpr=2" media="(max-width: 412px)" />
<source
data-srcset="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-websiteexample-thecrazymason-20240522-desktop.webp?crop=400:248,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=495&dpr=2" media="(max-width: 575px)" />
<img
class="lazyload"
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-websiteexample-thecrazymason-20240522-desktop.webp?crop=400:248,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=650&dpr=2"
width="650"
height="403"
alt="desktop screenshot of website The Crazy Mason"
/>
</picture></div></div><p
class="entry-website-detail website-detail-url">
<span
class="icon">
<img
