class="entry-text"><p>The mobile site is fairly well-optimized for the smaller screen, but the banner image doesn't make as much of an impression as on the desktop, as the image is much smaller with a thick black border around it. The mobile site maintains the high accessibility, SEO, and best practices scores, but only has a performance score of 47/100 on Google's PageSpeed Insights report.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div
