alt="desktop screenshot of website"
width="400"
height="248"
/></div>
<img
class="lightbox-thumbnail-magnifier"
src="/assets/images/icon-magnifying.svg"
alt="magnifying glass"
width="50"
height="50"
/></div><div
class="entry-text"><p>The desktop site makes good use of the space to include a lot of white space to create an easy user experience. While we appreciated the clearly defined floating menu, the logo could be more prominent to take readers to the home page.</p><p>According to Google's PageSpeed Insights report, the desktop site scores in the 90s for SEO, best practices, accessibility, and performance, with the performance score reaching 91/100.</p></div></div><h4>Mobile Review</h4><div
class="entry-website-mobile"><div
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-famous-milkshake-bar-20240528-mobile.webp"
