alt="desktop screenshot of website"
width="400"
height="248"
/></div>
<img
class="lightbox-thumbnail-magnifier"
src="/assets/images/icon-magnifying.svg"
alt="magnifying glass"
width="50"
height="50"
/></div><div
class="entry-text"><p>The desktop site encourages customers to scroll the site with a fun, animated hero banner and clean grid layout. The larger screen size helps to maintain a good balance of text, white space, and imagery for a pleasant browsing experience.</p><p>While the contrast issues lower the desktop site's accessibility score to 88/100, Google's PageSpeed Insights report awards the desktop site an overall performance score of 93/100.</p></div></div><h4>Mobile Review</h4><div
class="entry-website-mobile"><div
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-shake-therapy-20240528-mobile.webp"
