class="row"><div
class="col-12 faq-item"><h3 id=what-is-a-milkshake-website class="question">What is a milkshake website?</h3><div
class="answer"><p>A milkshake website advertises a company's milkshake products and, often, either franchising opportunities or hiring the company for catering. Milkshake websites frequently use bright color palettes to complement the business theme, or stark monochromatic color palettes to allow the milkshake photos to stand out.</p></div></div><div
